metadata.name: Portrait of the blue-eyed woman
metadata.description: For a moment, my anxiety left me, seeing her blue eyes for the first time, as if it were a dream and thinking not to find her again, fate had different plans for me. It was all a dream, her golden hair, her giant pupils, her beautiful skin. Someone who certainly can't be real, too ephemeral, perfect, was my most beautiful thought for less than a weekend
